'''苏美拉修道院'''({{lang-el|Μονή Παναγίας Σουμελά}})是一座位于[[土耳其|土耳其]][[特拉布宗|特拉布宗]][[马奇卡|马奇卡]]的[[正教会|正教会]]修道院。道院属于[[君士坦丁堡普世牧首|君士坦丁堡普世牧首]]管辖。每年吸引希腊、俄罗斯等正教会国家的游客前来朝圣。道院面朝阿尔坦德勒峡谷，坐落在1200米高的悬崖之上。道院建于公元[[386年|386年]]，时值罗马帝国[[狄奥多西一世|狄奥多西一世]]在位时期。<ref name="kultur">[https://web.archive.org/web/20070929121659/http://www.kultur.gov.tr/EN/BelgeGoster.aspx?17A16AE30572D313E603BF9486D4371D91FBF5F1F3911EBA Sümela Monastery] (Archived from September 29, 2007). Republic of Turkey Ministry of Culture and Tourism.</ref>在千余年的历史中，此院受到[[东罗马帝国|东罗马帝国]]、[[特拉布宗帝国|特拉布宗帝国]]及[[奥斯曼帝国|奥斯曼帝国]]历代帝王的保护与维修。1923年，由于希土人口交换，道院遭到废弃。1930年，火灾烧毁了道院的木造建筑。此后数十年间，道院经受了不时的盗劫与毁坏。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sumela.com/listingview.php?listingID=4 |title=存档副本 |access-date=2017-04-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161219000734/http://www.sumela.com/listingview.php?listingID=4 |archive-date=2016-12-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>2010年，土耳其政府许可了君士坦丁堡教会复兴道院中的[[事奉圣礼|事奉圣礼]]。<ref>{{cite web| last=''Euronews''| title=Rare Orthodox mass held at Turkish monastery| url=http://www.euronews.net/2010/08/15/rare-orthodox-mass-held-at-turkish-monastery/| accessdate=2011-04-14| archive-date=2010-10-18| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101018143752/http://www.euronews.net/2010/08/15/rare-orthodox-mass-held-at-turkish-monastery/| dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>[http://chiesa.espresso.repubblica.it/articolo/1344422?eng=y Dormition in Turkey. Liturgy on the Black Mountain] {{Wayback|url=http://chiesa.espresso.repubblica.it/articolo/1344422?eng=y |date=20100818125426 }}, [[Sandro_Magister|Sandro Magister]], retrieved from [[L'espresso|L'espresso]]</ref><ref>{{cite web| last=''Qantara.de''| title=Greek Orthodox Liturgy in Turkey: Uncovering the Country's Non-Muslim Cultural Heritage| url=http://en.qantara.de/wcsite.php?wc_c=8374| accessdate=2011-08-02| archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130618182530/http://en.qantara.de/wcsite.php?wc_c=8374| archive-date=2013-06-18| dead-url=yes}}</ref>2012年，土耳其政府出资修复了苏美拉道院。至2018年9月已完成了部分修复，特拉布宗当地政府称，在当年的前八个月中，修道院接待了约三十万名游客。<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.dailysabah.com/feature/2018/09/11/turkeys-sumela-monastery-to-open-its-doors-after-three-years-of-restoration|title=Turkey's Sümela Monastery to open its doors after three years of restoration|author=|date=2018-09-10|work=ANADOLU AGENCY|accessdate=2018-12-26|archive-date=2020-08-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200813175243/https://www.dailysabah.com/feature/2018/09/11/turkeys-sumela-monastery-to-open-its-doors-after-three-years-of-restoration|dead-url=no}}</ref>

